## WhiteListing TLDs by using BlackLists (AKA Reject TLDs that dont match)
\.+(?!(com|net|org|us|edu|mil|gov|io|im))$

## Testing Section
^metrics?[-.]

## Mmotti's List| Ref: https://github.com/mmotti/pihole-regex
^(.+[-_.])??[m]?ad[sxv]?[0-9]*[-_.]
^adim(age|g)s?[0-9]*[-_.]
^adse?rv(e(rs?)?|ices?)?[0-9]*[-.]
^adtrack(er|ing)?[0-9]*[-.]
^advert(s|is(ing|ements?))?[0-9]*[-_.]
^aff(iliat(es?|ion))?[-.]
^analytics?[-.]
^banners?[-.]
^beacons?[0-9]*[-.]
^count(ers?)?[0-9]*[-.]
^pixels?[-.]
^stat(s|istics)?[0-9]*[-.]o
^telemetry[-.]
^track(ers?|ing)?[0-9]*[-.]
^traff(ic)?[-.]

